data.description: Introducing an exquisite 1-story single-family home in the exclusive 55+ community of SOLIVITA. Featuring 2 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a den, thoughtfully designed to offer a blend of functionality and modern elegance. Upon entry, guests are greeted by an immaculately updated interior boasting waterproof laminate flooring, meticulously installed in 2022. This addition brings a contemporary touch to the living room, dining room, and well-appointed kitchen complete with a breakfast bar and convenient laundry room. Abundant natural light gracefully bathes these spaces, fostering a warm and inviting ambiance.    Notably, the home benefits from a newer roof, thoughtfully installed in 2017, ensuring a maintenance-free living experience. Freshly added fixtures and outlets throughout the residence further enhance its contemporary aesthetic, creating an environment that effortlessly caters to discerning tastes.    The allure of this property extends beyond its interior, beckoning residents to a private outdoor retreat. A charming patio awaits, providing an idyllic setting for serene relaxation. An added dimension of tranquility is found in the secluded backyard, shielded by a protected preserve, offering unparalleled privacy and serenity.    This property also features a noteworthy addition—a Cat 4 approved room, thoughtfully appointed with double plated glass windows. This versatile space can easily serve as a 3rd bedroom or a den, complete with a dedicated office area. With this addition, the total square footage of the home surpasses 2100 sq. ft., opening the door to a myriad of possibilities.    The residence is nestled within Solivita, an award-winning 55+ community spanning over 4200 acres of wetlands and lakes. An impressive 150,000 sq ft of state-of-the-art amenities and fitness facilities await residents, including 14 swimming pools, 2 heated spas, tennis courts, pickleball courts, shuffleboard, bocce ball, a billiards room, an art gallery, and 3 distinguished dining establishments. Furthermore, the community boasts 2 championship 18-hole golf courses, offering exceptional recreational opportunities.    Solivita stands as a testament to exceptional living and has garnered recognition as one of the premier communities in America. Conveniently located near Central Florida's renowned theme parks and its rich tapestry of experiences, Solivita offers a slice of paradise to its residents. Each day within this esteemed community is a celebration of life's finer aspects, with this residence serving as the cornerstone of your aspirations.    To explore the possibilities that await within this professional haven, please don't hesitate to contact us today. Your future awaits in this meticulously appointed home.
